cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about video segmentation using neural networks, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a novel convolutional gated recurrent unit, which is a type of neural network architecture, indicating that the paper may also fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with processing and analyzing multimedia data (cs.MM) and improving the performance of the network through parameter reduction (cs.NE).
